name: Harvey Milk
description:
Sometimes, we get requests to spin-off our website. That will never happen, but it hasn't stopped us from considering various variations, as well as who would make that spin-off's perfect score. Without further ado:

 AtheistOrNotAtheist.com: Ayn Rand
 BeardedOrNotBearded.com: Abraham Lincoln
 CrazyOrNotCrazy.com: Mike Tyson
 DeadOrNotDead.com: Francisco Franco
 EnglishOrNotEnglish.com: Bobby Moore
 FrenchOrNotFrench.com: Marcel Marceau
 GayOrNotGay.com: Harvey Milk
 HairyOrNotHairy.com: Sasqwatch
 ItalianOrNotItalian.com: Frank Sinatra
 JerseyOrNotJersey.com: Bruce Springsteen
 KlingonOrNotKlingon.com: Worf
 LiarOrNotLiar.com: Richard Nixon
 MustachedOrNotMustached.com: Tom Selleck
 NerdOrNotNerd.com: Bill Gates
 OrphanOrNotOrphan.com: Annie
 PolishOrNotPolish.com: Pope John Paul II
 QueenOrNotQueen.com: Elizabeth I
 RobotOrNotRobot.com: Bender
 SaintOrNotSaint.com: Mother Teresa
 TallOrNotTall.com: Kareem Abdul-Jabbar
 UzbekOrNotUzbek.com: Rustam Kasimdzhanov
 VampireOrNotVampire.com: Dracula
 WeirdOrNotWeird.com: Al Yankovic
 X-ManOrNotX-Man.com: Wolverine
 YuppieOrNotYuppie.com: Alex P. Keaton
 ZombieOrNotZombie.com: Jesus Christ

And you know what? Harvey Milk, brilliant man, fearless pioneer, Jew, comes pretty close to a perfect score on our REAL website as well.
